item.title: CVE-2023-40307|2023-09-28T13:55:49.371Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20privileges
item.description: An attacker with standard privileges on macOS when requesting administrator privileges from the application can submit input which causes a buffer overflow resulting in a crash of the application. This could make the application unavailable and allow reading or modification of data.
